==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
From interrogative and relative pronouns of French (''[[qui]]''), Italian (''[[che]]''), Portuguese (''[[que]]''), and Spanish (''[[quién]]'')

===Affix===
[[Category:Esperanto prefixes]]
'''ki-'''
# what-. (Interrogative/relative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix.)
===Derived terms===
* ''[[kiu]]'': '''what''' individual, [[who]]
* ''[[kio]]'': '''what''' object, [[what]]
* ''[[kia]]'': '''what''' kind of
* ''[[kies]]'': belonging to '''what'''
* ''[[kiel]]'': '''what''' manner/degree
* ''[[kie]]'': '''what''' place, [[where]]
* ''[[kiam]]'': '''what''' time, [[when]]
* ''[[kiom]]'': '''what''' quantity, how much
* ''[[kial]]'': '''what''' reason, [[why]]